Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.09,0:01:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神崎先生 当天来回 还这么有精神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我以前当新闻记者时的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要喝什么 若不马上写起来就会静不下心来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.93,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.83,0:01:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要喝什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那请给我杯咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 这…这是所谓的乱流吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有摸到什么奇怪的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.86,0:02:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣者如此明目张胆的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的报导管制也差不多快到极限了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.31,0:02:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然没有看见其有破坏行动 我们就暂缓出手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.42,0:02:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然采取被动的防守策略 不像是我们的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.16,0:03:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过先不提这个 现在我想说的是麻幌的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.36,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在她虽然解除武装 同化为一般市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她也是圣者所知晓的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.74,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以受到追踪的可能性也不低吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是麻幌的事 你就不必担心 我已经派史莱修过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.55,0:03:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该会帮我们将麻幌保护好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.92,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我多操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.35,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到 竟然会派史莱修去 首领您也真是太多虑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提起这件事的可是你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自己本来就很想去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.90,0:03:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.87,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这件事也不用花那么久的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.58,0:04:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假过了一半以后想每天的菜单还真是辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.19,0:04:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典 盂兰盆会夜市的小吃摊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 突然来找你商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 真是刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 互助会长 请进去里面坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你们慢慢谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.77,0:04:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…互助会长不是找我而是找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 盂兰盆会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.81,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 盂兰盆会 不过 不是普通的盂兰盆会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.01,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则 我这个有25年资历的互助会长也不会亲自出马了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.15,0:05:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在找的人 就是愿意在会场正中央舞台上跳舞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.96,0:05:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然绋立叮很大 但每年仅仅只有一人能上台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 每年只有一名少女可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说今年是麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在互助会的票选结果 麻幌是遥遥领先的第一名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.76,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 她的表情应该是很想去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.76,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以 有很多人比我更适合我怎么能越级上台呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是容貌而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.28,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要能一个人站在高处好几小时 持续跳着作为大家范本的舞蹈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.98,0:06:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若非有过人的毅力、体力 是无法胜任的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的年轻人一下子就喊累 还要我们付酬劳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.46,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 今年就是你 只有你能胜任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.83,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你拒绝的话 我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 式条老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以非常诚挚的心答应您的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太好了 太好了 那就期待你的舞蹈啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.28,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌应该很适合穿浴衣吧 哎呀 失礼失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得应该是放在这附近才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.67,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是穿过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以试穿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是伯母的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是买新的好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.66,0:07:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 请你也穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用啦 我穿便服就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.67,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行啦 难得的祭典 怎么可以只有我穿浴衣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优一定也很适合穿浴衣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你做什么 啊 那里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.39,0:07:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等洗过之后我再来稍作修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你三件都洗了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 趁这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次穿起来刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.72,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为只是简单地把袖子固定住 若变太小还可以恢复原状喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.26,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.06,0:08:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我得快点练习舞蹈才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在看我跳吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从左下方到右上方两手扬起的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料的困难耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌跳舞的时候别忘了笑容 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 我们该走啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.69,0:09:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会变成只有小栗看家耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.10,0:09:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然要它当看门狗有点靠不住 不过家里也没有什么好偷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.04,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫出我的辅助器具吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是无所谓啦 辅助器具是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SUMON THE FANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.62,0:09:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 麻幌 你这家伙过得还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说…说话了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.43,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你就是麻幌最爱的主人 阿优主人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.64,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是史莱修 麻幌最棒的仆人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.14,0:09:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是麻幌的主人 这样说来 你也算是我的主人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.78,0:10:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 美里司令的儿子 竟然如此畏畏缩缩 一点都不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟美里司令的事情还没有跟阿优说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情早说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.32,0:10:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我跟麻幌打算以平等的关系相处耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我去干掉谁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你和小栗看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.74,0:10:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 你要我充当看门狗顾家吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.18,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 因为小栗一个人太可怜 我希望你能陪陪它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当小狗的保母？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我说才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她越来越不像机械人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了 开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.58,0:11:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互助会的工作还真不轻松呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要跳几个小时呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前后加起来大约三个小时吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个小时？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.06,0:11:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那无懈可击 丝毫不差 完美正确的绋立舞蹈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷佛就是个天生的绋立女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这阵子特训过了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.44,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来盂兰盆会进入休息时间 大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.98,0:11:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 麻幌 跳得很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 托您的福 我也跳得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.36,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续跳了三小时十二分也没喘息过一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…真是不简单啊 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如同我所预期的 不 还更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.74,0:12:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年来没有见识过如此美丽的绋立舞蹈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.14,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有幸能接受如此大任 还让大家夸奖 我实在很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家的老伴也望尘莫及呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有约 我先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她果然很适合穿浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.07,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会 我跳得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.88,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家都到齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离烟火大会开始还有些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去逛逛夜市吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.69,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 这就是夜市啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.59,0:13:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是幢憬的夜市吗 阿优 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 麻幌 来吃炒面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.25,0:13:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种缠绕于嘴里的独特嚼劲 偶尔嚼到的高丽菜口感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及将这些全部掩盖的强劲酱汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是与海之家拉面匹敌的 无法分析的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吓我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你稍微体会到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太优秀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,极品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太出色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌真是的 她是不是有点幼儿化？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行喔 这么晚还夜游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,规定上不是写着晚上七点过后禁止外出吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来需要好好的处罚你一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 算帐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式条老师 冷…冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我一定要跟你做变态且危险的第一次接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.14,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要将这热泪的一晚 刻在你的身体上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校老师竟然是那德性 这个时代还真幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是羡慕现在的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湘…娶媳妇就娶绋立女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.81,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姿色好 本性好 品行好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.82,0:15:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个勤劳的圣洁少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一刻也不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 马上就诉诸暴力的行为 我觉得实在有待商榷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无须多言请反省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个对自己诚实的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要因为太过诚实 而失去了理性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(奖品)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.07,0:16:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光射中是不行的 要把它打下来才行呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太逊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 我可以用这把枪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不玩了 不玩了 不玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 今天已经要打烊了 要打烊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好现在结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(夜市捣蛋鬼)(一发现这两人请马上关店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.03,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(暴露狂 25至30岁)(外表看似高雅 其实本性凶残)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本没办法决胜负嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来总算逃脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有闻到酒臭味 不过千万不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这附近好像还蛮多人的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶…咦 那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是不是身体不舒服呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要去啦 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 他们看起来好像很困扰耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不困扰 不困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不困扰就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去那边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以清楚的了望街景喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.44,0:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.69,0:17:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心啦 只是阵雨罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.59,0:17:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边可以避雨喔 我们去那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是到那之前就会被淋湿 而且我想很快就会停了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二 跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样做会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 阿优 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 我已经好久没这么开心地来夏日祭典了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈去世…爸爸去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.39,0:19:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成孤单一个人以后来这种地方是很难受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃棉花糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.66,0:19:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是已经掉到地上 变得很难吃了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们再去买棉花糖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看烟火没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我要吃棉花糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有这种节庆就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.30,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 阿优 你看 又有个大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.03,0:20:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿优 麻幌 这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要喝一杯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了老师以外 大家都未成年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个是怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淋湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不冷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会 很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.08,0:20:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向往人类生活的机械人啊 她的心情我也不是不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在你旁边保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典真是好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明年我们也一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 希望明年还能再来

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.94,0:23:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于战士而言 生命的意义为何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.44,0:23:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们战士放弃了战争 即使只有一刹那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会被允许存在于这个世界的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.48,0:23:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练有素的战士互相搏斗的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.28,0:24:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓战士的生命 是存在于这其中刹那间的光芒 不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.29,0:24:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V1046-R麻幌 我要把这里变成战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.50,0:24:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直逼你的心
